data.Description: Do you want to get quick results? if you’re struggling with your mundane gym routine and feel like you’re just not getting the results you want. We aim to increase your ability in 10 components of fitness, Cardiovascular Endurance, Strength, Stamina, Agility, Flexibility, Balance, Power, Speed, Coordination and Accuracy. data.Description:
Optimum Performance is a group fitness fat loss program that uses our unique “Climb to the Peak” system of metabolic circuit training designed to challenge, inspire and transform your body. This program was designed with two main goals in mind; one, is to help YOU get in the best shape of YOUR life (lean, ripped, strong and fit) and two, to give the experienced exerciser an opportunity to take their fitness to a whole new level and break through plateaus that have kept their fitness results limited.

Meets for three months, twice a week.
